<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.1.10">
<l>kariya mukilpurai mēṉimāya ṉaikkaṇṭacu vaṭuraittu</l>
<l>puravi mukañceytu cennelōṅki viḷaikaḻa ṉipputuvai</l>
<l>tiruviṟ polimaṟaivā ṇaṉpaṭṭar pirāṉcoṉṉa mālaipattum</l>
<l>paravu maṉamuṭaip pattaruḷ ḷārpara maṉaṭicēr varkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who are devotees with hearts that praise [this]</l>
<l>garland of ten [verses] composed by the lord scholar learned</l>
<l rend="indent">in the Veda, in which prosperity flourishes,</l>
<l>in Putuvai with paddy fields that produce red paddy</l>
<l rend="indent">rising high [like] the heads of horses,</l>
<l>giving hints for seeing Māyaṉ </l>
<l rend="indent">with a body that resembles a black cloud,</l>
<l>they will reach with the feet of the Supreme.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
